# SPLICE E2E Testing - Premiere Pro

## Objective
Test every feature in Premiere Pro. Find bugs, fix them, verify fixes, repeat until clean.

## Test Protocol
```
1. Test feature → 2. Bug found? → 3. Fix it → 4. Retest → 5. Clean? → Next feature
```

## Key Files
```
splice-plugin/js/main.js          # Workflow orchestration, button handlers
splice-plugin/js/builder.js       # Sequence building, marker creation
splice-plugin/js/config.js        # API calls, backend URL
splice-plugin/js/settings.js      # License key activation, presets
splice-plugin/js/credits.js       # Credit display, usage tracking
splice-plugin/index.html          # UI elements, modals

splice-backend/server.js          # All API endpoints
splice-backend/services/          # 30 service files
```

## Features to Test

### 1. Authentication
- [ ] License key input (SPLICE-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX format)
- [ ] `/license/activate` returns customer ID
- [ ] Credits display after login
- [ ] Logout clears state

### 2. Silence Detection
- [ ] Preset dropdown works (podcast/interview/vlog/reaction/tutorial)
- [ ] Custom sensitivity slider
- [ ] `/silences-rms` returns segments
- [ ] Markers created in timeline

### 3. Take Detection
- [ ] `/analyze` transcribes audio
- [ ] Takes labeled with colors
- [ ] Best take highlighted
- [ ] J-Cut/L-Cut options

### 4. Cut List
- [ ] `/cut-list` generates v3.5 JSON
- [ ] Apply cuts to timeline
- [ ] Undo works correctly

### 5. Captions
- [ ] `/captions/templates` returns 5 styles
- [ ] Caption generation works
- [ ] Export SRT/VTT/JSON

### 6. Chapters
- [ ] `/chapters` detects segments
- [ ] Chapter markers in timeline
- [ ] YouTube timestamp format

### 7. Music Generation
- [ ] `/music/moods` loads options
- [ ] `/music/instruments` loads options
- [ ] Generate music (if credits available)
- [ ] Music library displays

### 8. Social Reframe
- [ ] `/reframe/platforms` loads (TikTok, Reels, etc.)
- [ ] Face detection works
- [ ] Safe zone overlay

### 9. Vocal Isolation
- [ ] `/isolate-vocals` processes audio
- [ ] Separated tracks returned

### 10. Text-Based Editing
- [ ] Transcript displays
- [ ] Delete text = delete video
- [ ] Sync with timeline

## API Health Checks
```bash
curl -sk https://127.0.0.1:3847/health
curl -sk https://127.0.0.1:3847/music/moods
curl -sk https://127.0.0.1:3847/captions/templates
curl -sk https://127.0.0.1:3847/reframe/platforms
curl -sk https://127.0.0.1:3847/export/formats
```

## Bug Report Format
```
Feature: [name]
Expected: [behavior]
Actual: [behavior]
File: [path:line]
Fix: [description]
```

## Final Verification
After all features pass:
1. Run `node tests/comprehensive-e2e.test.js`
2. Run `node tests/phase6-license.test.js`
3. Update CLAUDE.md with any changes
